Global Surgical Sheet Market Insights
Surgical Sheet Market size was valued at USD 1.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.15 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Surgical Sheet Market Overview
The global surgical sheet market is projected to reach USD 5.27 billion by 2030, up from USD 3.92 billion in 2023, reflecting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 4.3% during this period. Surgical sheets, including drapes, gowns, and sheets, are essential in maintaining sterility during surgical procedures, thereby preventing cross-contamination and bacterial transmission in healthcare settings. The increasing number of surgeries and the rising prevalence of hospital-acquired infections (HAIs) are key factors driving market growth. Additionally, the demand for disposable surgical sheets is expected to rise due to their convenience and effectiveness in infection control.

